data.description: Beautiful 3 flat in the heart of Old Monee! This building has been impeccably maintained and completely updated, including a new roof, windows, doors, siding, deck, and stairs. The First-floor unit was a commercial space converted into a large two-bedroom apartment with a big open living space.  The two upstairs units have one bedroom and have been updated. Each unit has its own high-efficiency ac compressor, furnace, and water heaters.   The Main floor was modified to have the back entrance, and bathroom size, and door opening to fit ADA requirements if buyers want to back to a commercial space.    Amazing location and is rarely vacant, a FANTASTIC investment opportunity!   Rental income/year $33,300 + $240 for Laundry
